decisions.description:
The main goal of this flow is to create an Event ( a type of Activity ). But we must create that Event within an existing record.
If all previous attempts at finding a record failed ( via SFID, or Invitee Email ): then we need to create a record.
We will always create a Lead when we couldn't find a record.
decisions.name: Do_we_have_a_Record
decisions.label: Do we have a Record?

decisions.description:
While looking up the records, if we found one, we would have set the OwnerId as the record owner.
In the last step, we attempted to overwrite the OwnerId with the id of the user whose email matches the publisher.
So at this point, we hope to have an owner defined. If we don't we'll have to look up the system admin.

If we cannot find the system admin profile, we cannot find the system admin. And if we're at this point in the logic, we have no other owner.
So there's no path forward if the profile is not found.

Flow.description:
Updated to include AU B2C calendly question order; Updated to include new AUS B2C round robin; Updated to include mobile phone number for ZA B2C; Added 'dylan.nedft@elevateeducation.com' for ZA B2C; Updated logic for changing application status based on product family; Updated 'alex.odonnell@elevateeducation.com' for UK B2C Tweaked Start Date/End Date criteria for mid funnel Tweaked mid funnel value to "Mid-Funnel Campaign" Updated Lead creation logic for mid funnel campaigns Updated B2C Lead pathway for UK (new question in Calendly) Updated B2C Lead pathway for AUS (new question in Calendly) Updated B2C Lead pathway for ZA Added Pre & Post webinar logic based on UTM links. Added 5 x UTM fields to Lead Creation steps for b2c Aus & UK. Added Molly & Jess emails for UK B2C pathway; Updated BU formula; New Lead pathway for UK
Created new 'LeadOwnerId' variable used to assign to a Lead.
Removed Create Campaign Member step (this logic has been moved after Pardot sync to LEAD AutoLaunch UpdatedOnly by B2BMAUser RunAfter)
Added logic to find Owner Id for b2c Leads for each region (Decision 'Which B2C SBU' & 3 x Get Records 'Find B2C Owner')
Creates event (activity) based on Calendly Events (Elevate's custom flow, based on Calendly's template) - updated Campaign filter start date, end date (to reference Current Date variable)
